	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />SMB3 uses 8x16 sprites.  I'm think the batman games use 8x16 sprites.  i'd figure older games would use 8x8 tiles since you couldn't really afford to waste tiles like celius said.  to add to the above post, 8x16 sprites means you also spend less cpu time writing OAM since there's less tiles to write when using larger sprites.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


