		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Contra uses 8x16 sprites, and so does Smash TV.
<br />
<br />But if you're using 8x16 sprites, you also have either bigger game objects or more game objects, which tends to cancel out the CPU reduction.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
