		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well, my main character is made of only 4 sprites when standing still now that I've used 8x16 sprites. He is 16 pixels wide and 32 tall. If I were to use 8x8, it would be 8 sprites, which seems like a really big waste. With 8x16 you just cut that in half.

		

		</td>
